-----------
-- climc --
-----------

* Required softwares *

  You will need :

  - asdf : http://www.cliki.net/asdf
  - mcclim :
  - cl-xmpp :

* ASDF *

  In /usr/share/common-lisp/systems, create a symbolic link
  to the system definition file (climc.asd)
  or
  add the Climc directory to *central-directory* of ASDF :
  (push "/directory/climc/" asdf:*central-registry*)

* Load *

  In the Lisp system :
  (asdf:operate 'asdf:load-op 'climc)

* Launch GUI *

 CL-USER> (climc:start-climc (cons "xxxxx@gmail.com" "xxxxxx")
                             '("contact1@gmail.com"
			       "contact2@gmail.com"))



